doc.previous: On 10 May 2014 Austria won the Eurovision Song Contest 2014 with the song Rise Like a Phoenix performed by Austrian drag artist Conchita Wurst This was their second win with their first being in 1966 Austria will now host the Eurovision Song Contest 2015 at Wiener Stadthalle in Vienna
